Third-Party Software Notices

The MIT license above applies to the WebToolBox source code in this
repository only. WebToolBox loads and runs the following third-party
components in the user's browser at runtime. They are fetched as prebuilt
WebAssembly/JavaScript bundles from the jsDelivr CDN and are NOT part of this
repository; each remains governed by its own license.

1. FFmpeg (via ffmpeg.wasm core, @ffmpeg/core)
   - License: GNU General Public License v2.0 or later (the ffmpeg.wasm core
     used here is built with GPL components enabled, including libx264, so
     the distributed binary is licensed under the GPL)
   - Website: https://ffmpeg.org
   - Source code: https://github.com/FFmpeg/FFmpeg
   - WebAssembly build: https://github.com/ffmpegwasm/ffmpeg.wasm
   - Fetched at runtime from:
     https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@ffmpeg/core@0.12.10/dist/umd

2. ffmpeg.wasm JavaScript wrapper (@ffmpeg/ffmpeg, @ffmpeg/util)
   - License: MIT
   - Source code: https://github.com/ffmpegwasm/ffmpeg.wasm

3. Gifsicle (via gifsicle-wasm-browser)
   - License: GNU General Public License v2.0
   - Website: https://www.lcdf.org/gifsicle/
   - Source code: https://github.com/kohler/gifsicle
   - WebAssembly build (wrapper licensed MIT):
     https://github.com/renzhezhilu/gifsicle-wasm-browser
   - Fetched at runtime from:
     https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/gifsicle-wasm-browser@1.5.16/dist/gifsicle.min.js

Complete corresponding source code for the GPL-licensed components is
available from the source repositories linked above. No modifications have
been made to these components; they are used as published.
